### ESP32 LED Ring API Test Requests
### Replace {{host}} with your ESP32 IP (e.g., http://192.168.1.241)

@host = http://192.168.1.241

### ==================== GET Endpoints ====================

### Get current status
GET {{host}}/status

###

### Get available animations
GET {{host}}/animations

### ==================== Animation Control ====================

### Set animation to solid
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "solid"}

###

### Set animation to fade
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "fade"}

###

### Set animation to strobe
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "strobe"}

###

### Set animation to spin
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "spin"}

###

### Set animation to spinTail
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "spinTail"}

### ==================== Color Control ====================

### Set color to RED
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#FF0000"}

###

### Set color to GREEN
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#00FF00"}

###

### Set color to YELLOW/ORANGE
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#FF9600"}

###

### Set color to BLUE
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#0000FF"}

###

### Set color to WHITE
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#FFFFFF"}

### ==================== Power Control ====================

### Turn ON
POST {{host}}/power
Content-Type: application/json

{"on": true}

###

### Turn OFF
POST {{host}}/power
Content-Type: application/json

{"on": false}

### ==================== Brightness Control ====================

### Set brightness to MAX (255)
POST {{host}}/brightness
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 255}

###

### Set brightness to MEDIUM (128)
POST {{host}}/brightness
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 128}

###

### Set brightness to LOW (50)
POST {{host}}/brightness
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 30}

### ==================== Animation Parameters ====================

### Set animation speed (ms per step)
POST {{host}}/speed
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 40}

###

### Set strobe period (ms for full on+off cycle)
POST {{host}}/strobe
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 100}

###

### Set tail length for spinTail (1-12)
POST {{host}}/tail
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 12}

### ==================== Per-Pixel Control ====================

### Set single pixel (position 0 = first LED)
POST {{host}}/pixel
Content-Type: application/json

{"position": 0, "rgb": "#FF0000"}

###

### Set single pixel (position 1)
POST {{host}}/pixel
Content-Type: application/json

{"position": 1, "rgb": "#00FF00"}

###

### Set single pixel (position 2)
POST {{host}}/pixel
Content-Type: application/json

{"position": 2, "rgb": "#0000FF"}

###

### Set multiple pixels at once (array format)
POST {{host}}/pixels
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"position": 0, "rgb": "#FF0000"},
  {"position": 1, "rgb": "#00FF00"},
  {"position": 2, "rgb": "#0000FF"}
]

###

### Set multiple pixels at once (object format)
POST {{host}}/pixels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pixels": [
    {"position": 0, "rgb": "#FFFFFF"},
    {"position": 1, "rgb": "#FF9600"},
    {"position": 2, "rgb": "#00FFFF"}
  ]
}

###

### Rainbow pattern (all pixels different colors)
POST {{host}}/pixels
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"position": 0, "rgb": "#FF0000"},
  {"position": 1, "rgb": "#FF7F00"},
  {"position": 2, "rgb": "#FFFF00"}
]

###

### All pixels same color (red)
POST {{host}}/pixels
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"position": 0, "rgb": "#FF0000"},
  {"position": 1, "rgb": "#FF0000"},
  {"position": 2, "rgb": "#FF0000"}
]

###

### Clear all pixels (set to black)
POST {{host}}/pixels
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {"position": 0, "rgb": "#000000"},
  {"position": 1, "rgb": "#000000"},
  {"position": 2, "rgb": "#000000"}
]

### ==================== Combined Effect Tests ====================

### Test: Red Strobe (like busy status)
# 1. Set color red
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#FF0000"}

###

# 2. Set strobe period
POST {{host}}/strobe
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 100}

###

# 3. Activate strobe animation
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "strobe"}

###

### Test: Solid Red (after strobe)
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "solid"}

###

### Test: Yellow Fade (like away status)
# 1. Set color yellow/orange
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#FF9600"}

###

# 2. Set fade speed
POST {{host}}/speed
Content-Type: application/json

{"value": 40}

###

# 3. Activate fade animation
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "fade"}

###

### Test: Solid Green (like available status)
# 1. Set color green
POST {{host}}/color
Content-Type: application/json

{"rgb": "#00FF00"}

###

# 2. Activate solid animation
POST {{host}}/animation
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "solid"}
